```python
def extract_product_names(texts):
    product_names = []
    for text in texts:
        words = text.split()
        potential_products = ["".join(comb) for comb in itertools.combinations(words, 2, maxlen=3)] + words
        product_names += list(set(potential_products))
    return product_names
```
